text: The Cup (ཕོར་པ། or Phörpa) is a 1999 Bhutanese Australian Nepalese sports comedy movie directed by Khyentse Norbu and starring Orgyen Tobgyal, Neten Chokling. It was distributed by Fine Line Features. ==Other websites== * Category:1999 comedy movies Category:1990s sports movies Category:Bhutanese movies Category:Australian comedy movies Category:Nepalese movies
